  "sections" : [ {
    "type" : "verse",
    "label" : "VERSE 1",
    "lines" : [ {
      "text" : "That God should love a sinner such as I,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 5
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 23
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 30
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 38
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Should yearn to change my sorrow into bliss,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 7
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 26
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 38
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Nor rest till He had planned to bring me nigh,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 4
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 21
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 32
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "How wonderful is love like this!",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 4
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 17
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 27
      } ]
    } ]
  }, {
    "type" : "chorus",
    "label" : "CHORUS",
    "lines" : [ {
      "text" : "Such love, such wondrous love, (2)",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 5
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 16
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 25
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "That God should love a sinner such as I,"
    }, {
      "text" : "How wonderful is love like this!"
    } ]
  }, {
    "type" : "verse",
    "label" : "VERSE 2",
    "lines" : [ {
      "text" : "That Christ should join so freely in the scheme,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 5
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 27
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 41
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Although it meant His death on Calvary,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 2
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 22
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 36
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Did ever human tongue find nobler theme",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 4
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 15
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 27
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Than love divine that ransomed me?",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 5
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 22
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 31
      } ]
    } ]
  }, {
    "type" : "verse",
    "label" : "VERSE 3",
    "lines" : [ {
      "text" : "That for a wilful outcast such as I,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 5
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 18
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 34
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "The Father planned, the Saviour bled and died;",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 4
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 24
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 41
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Redemption for a worthless slave to buy,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 2
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 17
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 27
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Who long had law and grace defied.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 4
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 21
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 29
      } ]
    } ]
  }, {
    "type" : "verse",
    "label" : "VERSE 4",
    "lines" : [ {
      "text" : "And now He takes me to His heart, a son,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 4
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 20
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 27
      } ]
    }, {
